# Understand the environments GOV.UK Sign In uses

GOV.UK Sign In uses 2 different environments:

* an integration environment, which contains sample users and data for you to test your service’s integration with GOV.UK Sign In
* a production environment, which is the live environment for real users to access and use your service’s integration with GOV.UK Sign In

## Understand and use the integration environment

Before you can use GOV.UK Sign In, you need to build a proof of concept client and explore the end-to-end journey in our integration environment. This will help you understand how to [integrate with GOV.UK Sign In](/how-govuk-sign-in-works/#integrate-with-gov-uk-sign-in), and where it will fit within your service. 

To get started, you’ll need to [choose the level of authentication for your service][choose auth].

